<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als Mangolt Amman und <expan cert="unknown">B.</expan> Kopp, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>, yeczunden czü <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
                        gnaden <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> von schulde wegen, die man in und
                                <expan>etlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> beleibt in <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        stat czü Lanczhüt, als sie <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> das <expan>selb<ex>er</ex></expan> erczelen
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>, also
                        <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir ewr gnad darczü wenden wöllet, daz
                                <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und auch
                            <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, wo die fürbas auch czü
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan>, ir schulde, was man in
                            <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add>doselbst czü Lanczhüt</add>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> rechts <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> beleibt,
                        gerichtet und beczalt <expan>w<ex>er</ex>de</expan>. Als etc. Das
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.</ab>
</div>
